      <elementaryExchange id="681214e4-2126-5b96-85f1-f1aed6ca48ff" unitId="487df68b-4994-4027-8fdc-a4dc298257b7" casNumber="014302-87-5" amount="2.38245787323089E-11" elementaryExchangeId="e1aa92d7-9297-452e-ade0-e5e2acc52ad7" formula="Hg+2">
        <name xml:lang="en">Mercury II</name>
        <unitName xml:lang="en">kg</unitName>
        <comment xml:lang="en">Emissions of heavy metals to ground water arise from leaching. These emissions are estimated  based on the SALCA-heavy metal model (Freiermuth 2006) following the procedure in the ecoinvent agricultural LCI tool (Faist Emmenegger, Délerce-Mauris and Porté 2018 Models Integrated in Ecoinvent LCI Calculation Tool for Crop Production).  The crop system carries a share of heavy metals emissions based on the ratio of cropping additions to total additions (additions to crop system divided by additions to crop system plus depostion from air and present in soils)Sources for heavy metals leaching to groundwater include: Leaching of heavy metals to groundwater (Wolfensberger &amp; Dinkel 1997), where no drainage is installed ; the share of leaching to groundwater is calculated from Drainage on all cropland acres state-wide, including tile drainage (57.9%,) and ditch drainage (7.0%). USDA (2018) 2017 Census of Agriculture, Volume 1, Chapter 2: State Level Data - Table 41.  Land Use Practices:  2017 and 2012 (live table: https://www.nass.usda.gov/Quick_Stats/CDQT/chapter/2/table/41/state/US). US Department of Agriculture (USDA). https://www.nass.usda.gov/Publications/AgCensus/2017/Full_Report/Volume_1,_Chapter_2_US_State_Level/st99_2_0041_0041.pdf.
(N.B. The uncertainty associated with manure data increases the uncertainty of the heavy metal emissions.)
Sources:
Freiermuth (2006) SALCA-Schwermetall - Modell zur Berechnung der Schwermetall- flüsse in der Landwirtschaftlichen Ökobilanz. Agroscope FAL Zürich-Reckenholz . https://www.agroscope.admin.ch/dam/agroscope/de/dokumente/themen/umwelt-ressourcen/produktionssysteme/salca-schwermetall.pdf.download.pdf/SALCA-Schwermetall.pdf 
